32:06.382 --> 32:07.425
[Kie] What?

32:12.013 --> 32:14.849
When... people get...

32:16.643 --> 32:17.810
close to me,

32:20.313 --> 32:21.481
I feel trapped.

32:22.815 --> 32:25.234
And... I bail.

32:26.778 --> 32:28.488
And then I blame them for it.

32:35.620 --> 32:37.038
I'm really sorry...

32:41.501 --> 32:44.003
[takes a deep breath] ...and I miss you.

32:50.843 --> 32:53.805
Do you think there's a chance
that we could be okay again?

32:53.888 --> 32:55.264
[Kie] Honestly...

32:57.475 --> 32:58.476
I don't know.

33:16.369 --> 33:17.412
Hey, Sarah.

33:21.040 --> 33:22.083
Hey, Kiara.

33:26.337 --> 33:28.589
Promise me that you won't bail on John B.

33:32.343 --> 33:33.469
He's not just...

33:35.013 --> 33:36.305
some other guy.

33:39.684 --> 33:41.811
And he really, really likes you.

33:45.356 --> 33:46.357
I won't.

33:49.485 --> 33:50.486
Promise me.

33:54.032 --> 33:55.116
I promise.

34:04.959 --> 34:06.419
[sighs]

34:08.796 --> 34:11.174
Also, I'm sorry I called the cops.

34:13.760 --> 34:15.303
-I knew it.
-[giggles]

34:15.386 --> 34:17.096
I knew it, you bitch!

34:17.180 --> 34:19.182
[both laughing]

34:19.766 --> 34:21.142
I told you!

34:24.270 --> 34:26.105
You-- you should've invited me.

34:26.189 --> 34:27.482
So you called the cops?

34:27.565 --> 34:28.900
-Yes!
-[laughs]

34:28.983 --> 34:30.151
[Pope] Uh-oh!

34:30.234 --> 34:32.653
-You forget your keys or something?
-[John B] You need a tow?

34:33.362 --> 34:35.907
Don't give them the satisfaction
of thinking this worked.

34:35.990 --> 34:38.785
-Absolutely not.
-[John B] You gotta admit it was funny.

34:40.078 --> 34:41.621
-[Kie] John B.
-[John B] Uh, what's that?

34:42.121 --> 34:44.916
-[Kie] Mastermind, huh?
-I'm always plannin'.

34:45.500 --> 34:48.169
-Some patriarchal bullshit.
-[Sarah] Yeah, that sucked.

34:48.252 --> 34:49.879
You still love us though, right?

34:49.962 --> 34:50.797
Here.

34:51.255 --> 34:53.299
-[Sarah] Yeah, whatever.
-Hey, you still hate me?

34:53.382 --> 34:56.010
A little. We're both gonna get you back
when you least expect it.

34:56.094 --> 34:57.678
-Watch your back, boys.
-Mm-hm.

34:57.762 --> 34:59.806
-[Pope] I welcome that challenge.
-[JJ] Me too.

35:00.389 --> 35:02.016
So, did you guys, you know...

35:02.100 --> 35:03.601
Reconcile our differences?

35:04.519 --> 35:06.437
-Mm-mm.
-Not even close.

35:06.521 --> 35:10.233
-But we're... willing to work together.
-Mm.

35:10.733 --> 35:12.902
-[John B] You know what? That's victory.
-[JJ] Yep.

35:12.985 --> 35:13.945
Wiggedy-wiggedy-wiggedy!

35:14.028 --> 35:16.030
-[JJ] Know why? Hydroponic.
-[Pope] Don't say that.

35:16.114 --> 35:18.533
All right, shut up.
You guys ready to jack someone up?

35:19.575 --> 35:20.409
[Kie] Yeah, whatever.

35:20.493 --> 35:22.036
-[Sarah] Yep.
-In the boat.

35:22.120 --> 35:23.162
[JJ] Let's get it. 

35:25.832 --> 35:27.333
-[John B] You got rope?
-[Pope] Got it.

35:27.416 --> 35:29.460
-[John B] Grappling hook?
-[Pope] No grappling hook.

35:29.544 --> 35:30.503
We're not Batman.

35:31.754 --> 35:32.964
-[John B] Pulley?
-[Kie] Check.

35:33.047 --> 35:33.923
[John B] Dark clothes?

35:34.006 --> 35:35.591
-[Sarah] Got it.
-[John B] Flashlights?

35:35.675 --> 35:37.176
-[JJ] Check.
-[John B] All right, good.

35:37.260 --> 35:38.678
-We're ready.
-[Kie] Let's go.

35:38.761 --> 35:40.346
[JJ] Let's go get rich, guys.

35:40.638 --> 35:41.889
[Kie] Yeah. Hell, yeah.

35:45.309 --> 35:46.769
-[Sarah] Go, boys.
-[Kie] And girls.

35:46.853 --> 35:48.271
-[Pope] Let's go.
-[JJ] Let's roll.

35:48.354 --> 35:49.564
-[Sarah] Right on.
-Wait, wait

35:52.608 --> 35:54.694
I wanna say thank you, guys. Seriously.

35:55.945 --> 35:57.864
It means a lot to me
that you're here tonight.

36:00.324 --> 36:01.200
Always.

36:02.118 --> 36:03.411
[chuckles softly]

36:03.494 --> 36:04.620
Of course, man.

36:05.204 --> 36:06.122
My man.

36:09.083 --> 36:11.586
All right, we done with the circle jerk?
Can we go do this?

36:12.086 --> 36:14.297
-Yeah.
-[Pope] Let's get that wheat in the water.

36:14.380 --> 36:17.216
-[JJ] Weed? I'm up for weed.
-[Pope] Wheat. I said wheat.

36:17.300 --> 36:19.218
-[Kie] After you.
-[Sarah] Ladies first.

36:19.302 --> 36:20.178
[Kie] Alley-oop.

36:41.490 --> 36:43.034
-[Sarah gasps] Shit!
-[John B] Oh, shit!

36:43.117 --> 36:44.410
-Go, go, go, go.
-Flashlights!

36:44.493 --> 36:46.078
-[JJ] It's on strobe!
-[Kie] Flashlights.

36:46.162 --> 36:47.163
-[JJ panting]
-Shh!

36:47.246 --> 36:48.164
Okay...

36:48.789 --> 36:52.126
Okay, so she has motion sensor lights.

36:53.127 --> 36:55.880
We could, uh... move really slowly, maybe?

36:55.963 --> 36:57.340
-What?
-That's not how it works.

36:57.423 --> 37:00.426
-Oh, shit. Let's throw a rock at it.
-[Pope] What?

37:00.509 --> 37:03.304
That's a really good idea.
Let the axe murderer know that we're here.

37:03.387 --> 37:05.598
-Throw a rock at it?
-[John B] You have a better idea?

37:05.681 --> 37:07.183
Literally anything but that.

37:07.266 --> 37:10.019
What about the breaker?
In the circuit box on the porch.

37:10.102 --> 37:12.146
We used to play
hide-and-seek here as kids.

37:12.230 --> 37:14.732
And if we were brave enough,
we'd go all the way up to the porch.

37:15.524 --> 37:16.359
I've seen it.

37:16.442 --> 37:18.778
No, no.
You're not going in the house alone.

37:19.278 --> 37:20.112
Watch me.

37:20.196 --> 37:22.281
Crain chops people into pieces.

37:22.365 --> 37:24.408
If you believe that,
but she's like what, 85?

37:24.492 --> 37:27.161
-[JJ] Yeah, somethin' like that.
-She's probably barely still kicking.

37:27.662 --> 37:28.955
Here. I'll go with you.

37:29.705 --> 37:31.290
-Yeah.
-[Pope] We'll wait for your signal.

37:32.166 --> 37:35.628
-[Sarah] Okay, cool.
-[John B] Hey! Be safe.

37:36.295 --> 37:37.213
[Sarah] We will.

37:39.799 --> 37:41.884
-Be safe.
-I'll be so safe.

37:42.301 --> 37:44.637
-I'll be safe for you.
-[John B] Can you guys stop? Stop!

37:45.763 --> 37:46.806
I'm gonna kill you.

37:47.348 --> 37:49.141
But how would that keep us safe?

37:58.359 --> 38:01.779
[Sarah] She must have a generator
plugged into the main power supply.

38:05.992 --> 38:08.286
-[Kie gasps]
-Shh...

38:20.423 --> 38:21.632
[Sarah] Where are the breakers?

38:21.716 --> 38:22.591
What is this?

38:22.675 --> 38:24.135
No, no, no, no, no, no, no.

38:24.468 --> 38:25.594
Shit.

38:27.013 --> 38:28.264
[Sarah] It goes inside.

38:42.611 --> 38:44.363
[door creaking]

38:45.948 --> 38:49.660
-[JJ] They said when Hollis disappeared--
-That you should shut the eff up!

38:51.412 --> 38:52.413
[JJ whistles]

39:03.257 --> 39:05.134
[cat yowling]

39:05.217 --> 39:06.218
[glass tinkling]

39:11.766 --> 39:12.641
[Kie] Hey.

39:13.893 --> 39:14.977
[Sarah] Yeah. Yeah.

39:15.353 --> 39:16.479
Yeah.

39:25.154 --> 39:26.572
-[both chuckle softly]
-[Sarah] Oh.

39:26.655 --> 39:27.907
-All right.
-[Sarah] Okay.

39:27.990 --> 39:29.241
[switch clicks]

39:31.994 --> 39:33.996
-[switch clicks]
-[generator powers down]

39:36.874 --> 39:38.417
They did it. Go time.

39:38.501 --> 39:39.460
[Pope] So, let's do it.

39:39.543 --> 39:41.128
[John B] Three, two...

39:42.296 --> 39:43.631
Just-- just-- just go.

39:57.853 --> 39:59.772
[JJ] Holy crap, you know what this is?

39:59.855 --> 40:00.981
It just hit me.

40:01.065 --> 40:02.066
Pope, look.

40:02.983 --> 40:04.860
This is <i>C.H.U.D.</i> Full <i>C.H.U.D.</i>

40:05.319 --> 40:06.320
What is he talking about?

40:06.404 --> 40:08.697
Cannibalistic humanoid
underground dwellers?

40:09.156 --> 40:10.449
Have you guys not seen that film?

40:10.533 --> 40:11.951
-[John B] No.
-Can't say I have, no.

40:12.034 --> 40:13.035
It's actually a good film.

40:13.119 --> 40:14.954
It's about cannibals
that live in the sewers

40:15.037 --> 40:16.789
and under New York City, and it's like--

40:16.872 --> 40:18.207
[John B] Shut up! Shut up!

40:19.375 --> 40:21.460
All right.
How deep do you think this is, Pope?

40:21.919 --> 40:22.920
[sighs] I don't know.

40:25.423 --> 40:26.757
[whirring]

40:26.841 --> 40:28.008
[Sarah gasps]

40:29.593 --> 40:30.428
Shit.

40:36.767 --> 40:38.394
Hey, boys. I have one request.

40:38.477 --> 40:39.562
-[JJ] Yeah?
-Yeah?

40:39.645 --> 40:40.938
Don't drop me.

40:41.063 --> 40:42.773
-[JJ] Whoa!
-[yells] Okay...

40:42.857 --> 40:45.192
-You're gonna die first, for sure.
-Got ya.

40:45.276 --> 40:47.778
All right, just keep payin' it out
nice and slow like that.

40:50.990 --> 40:52.575
Here we go. Keep goin'.

40:55.661 --> 40:57.329
[grunting]

41:00.958 --> 41:02.001
Keep goin'.

41:05.087 --> 41:07.006
Wait, hold on one second.
I'm gonna get situated.

41:07.089 --> 41:07.965
[Pope] You good?

41:08.424 --> 41:09.467
[gasps] Oh, my--

41:09.550 --> 41:11.719
-Oh, shit! John, shit!
-[John B] Whoa! What--

41:11.802 --> 41:13.053
[JJ grunts] Jesus!

41:14.513 --> 41:16.140
[groans]

41:16.557 --> 41:20.269
-[grunting] John B!
-I told you not to drop me!

41:20.352 --> 41:21.854
-[clank]
-[gasps]

41:26.609 --> 41:29.236
-You good, man?
-[John B] What the hell was that?

41:29.320 --> 41:30.696
Little technical difficulties.

41:31.822 --> 41:33.115
Keep going, slow!

41:33.199 --> 41:35.326
Okay, we're gonna start
paying you out again, all right?

41:36.911 --> 41:38.621
[breathing heavily]

41:39.455 --> 41:40.956
[wind whistling]

41:45.377 --> 41:47.213
[Mrs. Crain wheezing, coughs]

41:51.884 --> 41:53.886
[shuffling and thumping]

41:56.096 --> 41:57.431
[breathing heavily]

42:00.601 --> 42:01.602
Shit.

42:01.685 --> 42:03.812
-[thumping]
-[heavy breathing]

42:05.147 --> 42:06.649
[John B breathing shakily]

42:08.400 --> 42:11.403
Okay. Okay. All right, keep goin'.

42:11.487 --> 42:13.531
[grunts] All right. Keep it comin'.

42:14.031 --> 42:15.991
[exhales, grunts] Okay.

42:16.075 --> 42:17.076
[Pope groans]

42:17.159 --> 42:19.787
Hey. Hey, we got 15 feet left.

42:19.870 --> 42:22.873
-Are you getting close to the bottom?
-[John B] I can't tell.

42:23.207 --> 42:25.000
-Just-- just keep goin'.
-Give me more.

42:25.084 --> 42:26.168
Yeah...

42:32.716 --> 42:34.093
Whoa! Stop!

42:35.886 --> 42:39.014
I'm hangin' over
some sewage-water lookin' shit.

42:39.098 --> 42:40.516
[Pope] You want back up?

42:40.599 --> 42:42.142
Keep goin', I guess...

42:42.601 --> 42:43.561
[JJ] Nice and slow.

42:48.315 --> 42:49.358
[John B] Here we go.

42:51.277 --> 42:52.236
Okay.

42:52.778 --> 42:53.946
Oh.

42:55.990 --> 42:59.034
[breathing shakily]

43:01.662 --> 43:03.706
Okay, okay! I'm at bottom.

43:04.915 --> 43:05.916
How is it down there?

43:07.001 --> 43:08.335
It's worse than I thought.

43:09.336 --> 43:12.172
-[thumping]
-[Mrs. Crain] It's-- it's late, Leon.

43:13.966 --> 43:16.719
Too late. [coughing]

43:16.802 --> 43:19.888
-You find any gold?
-[John B] Uh, nothin' yet.

43:21.849 --> 43:22.808
Wait.

43:23.892 --> 43:25.936
I think I felt something with my foot.

43:29.148 --> 43:31.150
[exhales] Here goes nothin'.

43:31.483 --> 43:32.735
[takes a deep breath]

43:38.407 --> 43:41.076
[gasps, coughing]

43:44.872 --> 43:46.206
Mr. Crain.

43:46.290 --> 43:48.459
[yelling] JJ! Hey, pull me up!

43:48.542 --> 43:51.420
-Pull me up! Come on, man! Go!
-[Pope] Pull him up! Come on, pull him up!

43:51.503 --> 43:52.838
[John B] Go! Come on! Pull me up!

43:52.921 --> 43:55.007
Come on! Pull me up! Pull me up!

43:55.799 --> 43:57.092
Come on! [gasping]

43:58.844 --> 43:59.678
Shit!

44:01.180 --> 44:02.931
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait! Wait!

44:09.605 --> 44:11.315
Hey, I think I found something.

44:11.398 --> 44:12.691
Hey, John B!

44:13.442 --> 44:16.362
-What'd you say?
-[John B] Just give me a minute. Hold on.

44:20.949 --> 44:22.159
[gasps]

44:23.243 --> 44:24.662
Okay. Okay.

44:24.745 --> 44:26.497
[breathes deeply]

44:32.586 --> 44:35.089
[grunting]

44:35.172 --> 44:37.508
-[Sarah and Kie breathing heavily]
-Hm.

44:40.094 --> 44:42.096
[Mrs. Crain] I can hear you, Leon.

44:42.179 --> 44:43.806
-[whimpers]
-I've been waiting all night!

44:43.889 --> 44:45.224
-[Sarah screams]
-[Kie] Go!

44:45.307 --> 44:46.183
Go! Go!

44:46.266 --> 44:48.268
[both panting]

44:49.853 --> 44:52.940
-[Mrs. Crain screeches] Leon!
-[Kie] Shit!

44:53.399 --> 44:55.567
-Shit!
-[Mrs. Crain] Where are you, Leon?

44:56.485 --> 44:57.403
Huh?

44:57.486 --> 44:58.362
[Kie] Come on...

44:59.279 --> 45:00.447
[gasping]

45:03.409 --> 45:05.035
[JJ, echoing] John B, you okay?

45:05.911 --> 45:06.995
Any dead bodies?

45:10.374 --> 45:11.417
[John B] Shit...

45:14.211 --> 45:15.671
[grunting]

45:39.403 --> 45:40.654
[metal scrapes]

45:52.124 --> 45:54.126
[breathing shakily]

45:57.671 --> 45:58.839
We did it, Dad.

46:00.340 --> 46:01.175
[Kie gasping]

46:02.217 --> 46:03.177
Oh!

46:03.260 --> 46:04.470
-Oh! Oh!
-[yelling]

46:04.553 --> 46:05.929
-[thumping]
-[Kie grunts]

46:06.013 --> 46:08.599
-[plates smash]
-[Mrs. Crain screeching]

46:08.682 --> 46:10.058
-[Sarah] Okay... [screams]
-[yells]

46:10.142 --> 46:11.977
-[whimpers]
-[fire poker clatters]

46:12.060 --> 46:13.812
-[Sarah] Come on, this way!
-[Kie] Okay.

46:14.271 --> 46:15.939
Okay. [yelps]

46:21.653 --> 46:22.863
-[Mrs. Crain yells]
-[both gasp]

46:22.946 --> 46:24.239
-[Sarah] Shit!
-[wood smashing]

46:24.323 --> 46:26.617
[Sarah] This way!
It goes underneath the house!

46:26.950 --> 46:28.952
[Mrs. Crain screeching]

46:36.335 --> 46:38.128
-[Kie] Go, go, go, go!
-[Sarah] I'm trying!

46:38.212 --> 46:39.171
-[Kie] Go!
-[Sarah] Guys!

46:39.254 --> 46:40.297
-[Kie] Guys!
-[Sarah] Guys!

46:40.380 --> 46:42.382
-What's going on?
-[Kie] Mrs. Crain! She's up there!

46:42.466 --> 46:43.967
She tried to kill us with a fire poker.

46:44.051 --> 46:45.844
-We gotta go.
-We locked her in the parlor,

46:45.928 --> 46:47.221
-but we gotta go.
-Okay, code red.

46:47.304 --> 46:49.765
-[Sarah] We have to go!
-Let's go. John B! Get back on, man!

46:49.848 --> 46:51.433
-[Pope] Hey!
-[John B] JJ!

46:51.517 --> 46:52.684
Hold on, man! I'm comin'!

46:53.101 --> 46:55.103
-[Sarah] Come on!
-[Pope] Three, two, one, pull!

46:55.187 --> 46:56.188
-[JJ] Jeez.
-[Sarah] Shit!

46:56.271 --> 46:57.397
[grunts]

46:57.481 --> 46:58.941
-[Pope] Where the hell is he?
-Shit.

46:59.024 --> 47:00.150
-Sh! Sh!
-[JJ] John B!

47:00.234 --> 47:01.276
-[Pope] Hey!
-Guys. Sh!

47:01.360 --> 47:03.195
[John B yells] I found the gold!

47:03.862 --> 47:04.947
[JJ] What's he saying?

47:05.364 --> 47:07.658
[John B, echoing] JJ! Pope! Kie!

47:07.741 --> 47:09.993
-Yo, he's drowning! We gotta pull him up!
-John B!

47:10.077 --> 47:13.455
Hey, John B! Get back on the rope.
We're gonna pull you back up, okay, buddy?

47:13.539 --> 47:14.998
-[Mrs. Crain wheezing]
-[Kie] Come on!

47:15.082 --> 47:16.667
-[Sarah] Come on! Pull!
-[JJ] Come on.

47:16.750 --> 47:18.836
-[JJ] Okay, everybody, help!
-[Kie] Guys!

47:19.628 --> 47:20.504
[John B] Okay, I'm on!

47:20.587 --> 47:21.547
-[Kie] Guys!
-Yeah! Yeah!

47:21.630 --> 47:24.591
-[JJ] Okay.
-[Pope] Let's go. [grunting]

47:25.342 --> 47:27.135
[Sarah and Kie groaning]

47:30.639 --> 47:31.849
[Pope groans] Come on!

47:31.932 --> 47:33.058
[yells]

47:33.141 --> 47:34.184
-[Pope] Pull!
-[gunshot]

47:34.268 --> 47:35.227
-[Kie] Shit!
-[JJ] Jesus!

47:35.310 --> 47:36.645
-[Kie] Shit!
-[JJ] Shit! Hang on!

47:36.728 --> 47:38.814
-[Pope yells]
-[John B] Pope! JJ! What the hell?

47:38.897 --> 47:41.984
-[JJ] Climb up! Help me! Hang on!
-[Pope groans] Tie it up now, man!

47:42.067 --> 47:43.318
[JJ] Pope, hide!

47:45.112 --> 47:46.780
[Kie yells] Go! Go!

47:46.864 --> 47:48.156
[both panting]

47:48.824 --> 47:50.826
-She can't aim for shit.
-She can't see.

47:51.660 --> 47:52.536
She's blind.

47:52.619 --> 47:53.996
-[gunshot]
-[Kie screams] Shit! Go!

47:54.079 --> 47:55.122
-Go, Sarah!
-[shotgun cocks]

47:55.205 --> 47:56.206
[Kie yells]

47:59.251 --> 48:01.253
[John B grunts, panting]

48:04.923 --> 48:06.717
-[gunshot]
-Go! Go!

48:06.800 --> 48:09.052
-Go! Go!
-I don't care if she is, that's buckshot!

48:10.554 --> 48:12.931
["Police on My Back" playing]

48:15.976 --> 48:17.311
[John B] Whoo!

48:17.394 --> 48:19.897
[chuckling] JJ! Pope! Kie! Yeah!

48:20.772 --> 48:22.065
[JJ] Can we go now?

48:23.400 --> 48:25.277
-[Sarah] Get into the car!
-[JJ] Come on!

48:25.360 --> 48:26.486
<i>♪ I'm runnin'... ♪</i>

48:26.570 --> 48:28.363
-[Sarah] Get to the car!
-[Pope] Go! Go!

48:28.447 --> 48:29.990
<i>♪ I've been hidin' ♪</i>

48:30.073 --> 48:31.533
<i>♪ Police on my back ♪</i>

48:31.617 --> 48:33.368
<i>-♪ There was a shootin'... ♪</i>
-[gunshot]

48:33.452 --> 48:35.579
-[Kie] Where is he?
-[Pope] Come on, start the car. Go!

48:35.662 --> 48:36.914
-[gunshot]
-[Kie] John B!

48:36.997 --> 48:39.875
-[Pope] Why are we always getting shot at?
-[Kie] Come on! John B, run!

48:40.709 --> 48:43.253
-Come on! Come on!
-[Pope] Wait! Wait, wait, wait, wait!

48:43.337 --> 48:44.546
-[Kie] Get in!
